sql_json.natural_language: Get the latest payment-related message from accounts@toscant.co.za to our accounts team.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM `email_search_index` WHERE fromEmail = 'accounts@toscant.co.za' AND 'accounts' IN UNNEST(toPeople) AND LOWER(subject) LIKE '%payment%' ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
